Description

Will Ferrell "Mustafa" fez, Ray-Ban sunglasses and lifecast from Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me. (New Line, 1999) Includes a plaster life cast of Will Ferrell's face and neck. From Will Ferrell's second appearance as his mysterious (and accident-prone) character. From the highly successful Austin Powers franchise and one of America's favorite comedians at an early stage in his movie career.
